      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis power-law model selection justified against physics of CPB flow.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen hemolysis power law selected based on published literature for blood pump CFD. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2 but model selection rationale is documented."
    },
    {
